[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to increase the Capital and amend the Powers of the Portsea Island Gaslight Company.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for making a Railway from the Ulster Railway near Lisburn to the Belfast and Northern Counties Railway at Antrim, to be called "The Dublin and Antrim Junction Railway," and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for enabling the London and North-western Railway Company to acquire additional Lands in connexion with their Chester and Holyhead Railway; for renewing certain Powers as to Steamboats; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to empower the Penarth Harbour, Dock, and Railway Company to raise a further Sum of Money; to make a Road between their Harbour and Cardiff; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for authorizing the Abandonment of the Thames Haven Dock and the Dissolution of the Company, and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the Sittingbourne and Sheerness Railway Company to raise additional Capital; to alter, amend, and repeal some of the Provisions of the Acts relating to the Company; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for enabling the London and North-western Railway Company to construct Railways from Edgehill to near Bootle, from Winwick to Golborne, and from Aston to Ditton, with a Branch to Runcorn; to enlarge their Lime Street and Wapping Stations at Liverpool; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for enabling the London and North-western Railway Company to construct Railways from Eccles through Tyldesley to Wigan, with a Branch to Bedford and Leigh; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to authorize the Fife and Kinross Railway Company to raise additional Capital.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to empower the North London Railway Company to widen a Portion of their Railway; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for vesting the Birkenhead Railway in the London and North-western Railway Company and the Great Western Railway Company, and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to authorize the South Staffordshire Railway Company to reuse additional Capital; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for making a Railway from the Londonderry and Enniskillen Railway in the County of Tyrone to the Town of Bundoran in the County of Donegal, and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the Midland Railway Company to make Railways from the Leeds and Bradford Line of their Railway to Otley and Ilkley in the West Riding of the County of York; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to provide for the future Election of Commissioners, to confirm certain Acts of the present Commissioners, and to consolidate in One Act the various Provisions for the Management and Regulation of the Port and Harbour of New Ross in the Counties of Wexford and Kilkenny.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the North-eastern Railway Company to construct Branch Railways between Arthington, Otley, and Ilkley; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to authorize the Construction of a Railway from the Great Southern and Western Railway near Parsonstown to Portumna Bridge on the River Shannon, and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for incorporating the West Cheshire Railway Company, and for authorizing them to make and maintain Railways from Northwich to Helsby; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for reviving the Powers of the Rhymney Railway Company with respect to their Bargoed Rhymney Branch Railway, and for authorizing them to raise further Monies; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to incorporate the City of Glasgow Life Assurance Company, and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the Great Southern and Western Railway Company to make a Railway from Roscrea in the County of Tipperary to Birdhill in the same County; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for the better Drainage of the Greetwell District in the County of Lincoln.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the Manchester and Milford Railway Company to construct a Branch Railway from the Devil's Bridge to Aberystwith; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for extending the Limits within which the Grand Junction Waterworks Company may supply Water, and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to confer additional Powers upon the Wolverhampton New Waterworks Company; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the Great North of Scotland Railway Company to enlarge their Stations at Kittybrewster and at Aberdeen, and to alter the Line and Levels of their Dock Branch.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to make better Provision for supplying with Water the Town and Township of Blackburn, and the Townships of Lower Darwen, Livesey, Witton, Oswaldtwistle, and Little Harwood; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to authorize the Construction in Lincolnshire of a Railway from the River Trent across the River Ancholme to the Manchester, Sheffield, and Lincolnshire Railway.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for enabling the Stockton and Darlington Railway Company to raise additional Capital; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for the Amalgamation of the Leven and East of Fife Railway Companies.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the Leven and Fast of Fife Railway Companies to extend the East of Fife Railway to Anstruther.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for the draining of Lands in Airedale, adjoining and near to the River Aire, in the West Riding of the County of York; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the Londonderry and Lough Swilly Railway Company to extend their Railway to Buncrana in the County of Donegal.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to authorize the Swansea Vale Railway Company to make certain new Railways; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the Dumfries, Lochmaben, and Lockerby Junction Railway Company to divert their authorized Line of Railway; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for making a Railway from the Great Western Railway to Hammersmith, to be called "The Hammersmith and City Railway," and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for the Enlargement, Regulation, and Management of "The Citadel Station" at Carlisle, situate at the Junction of the Lancaster and Carlisle and the Caledonian Railways, and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to authorize the Construction of a Railway from the Berks and Hants Extension Railway to Marlborough in Wiltshire.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for making a Railway from the Limerick and Foynes Railway to the Town of Newcastle in the County of Limerick, to be called "The Rathkeale and Newcastle Junction Railway," and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for the Extension of the South Yorkshire Railway across the Trent near Keadby in Lincolnshire, and for granting further Powers to the South Yorkshire Railway and River Dun Company.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for better supplying with Gas the Borough of Wigan and other Places adjacent thereto in the County Palatine of Lancaster.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to grant further Powers to the Waveney Valley Railway Company as to their Capital.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the Lord Mayor, Aldermen, and Burgesses of Dublin to construct additional Waterworks; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for the further Improvement of the Borough of Bolton, and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for making a Railway from the London, Brighton, and South Coast Railway at Uckfield in the County of Sussex to Tunbridge Wells in the County of Kent, and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for incorporating the Stockport, Timperley, and Altrincham Railway Company, and for authorizing them to make and maintain the Stockport, Timperley, and Altrincham Railway; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for altering and amending the Constitution of the Burgh of Hawick; extending the Boundaries thereof; maintaining an efficient System of Police therein; improving the said Burgh; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the Kinross-shire Railway Company to make certain Branch Railways; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to authorize the Construction of a Railway from the Eastern Counties Railway to Saffron Walden in Essex.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for enabling the Conway and Llanrwst Railway Company to make a Deviation and Alteration of their authorized Line of Railway; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to grant further Powers to the East Suffolk Railway Company; to authorize certain Arrangements with respect to their Share Capital; and to amend the Acts relating to the Company.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for making Railways from Aberystwith to various Places in the Counties of Cardigan, Montgomery, Merioneth, and Carnarvon, to be called "The Aberystwith and Welsh Coast Railways," and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for making a Railway from Bishop Stortford through Dunmow to Braintree, with a Branch therefrom, and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] relating to the Cleveland Railway; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the Forest of Dean Central Railway Company to construct further Works; and for other Purposes connected with their Undertaking.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to amend the Hatfield Chase Warping and Improvement Act, 1854.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for making a Railway from Forres to Birnam near Dunkeld, with a Branch to Aberfeldy, to be called "The Inverness and Perth Junction Railway;" and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for making a Railway to be called "The Ludlow and Clee Hill Railway," and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for making a Railway to improve the Communication between Salisbury and the Southern Part of the County of Dorset, and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the Vale of Clwyd Railway Company to raise additional Capital.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the Ware, Hadham, and Buntingford Railway Company to make a Deviation in the authorized Line of their Railway; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to authorize the Construction of a Railway from Holme to Ramsey in the County of Huntingdon.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for making a Railway from the Stirling and Dunfermline Railway to the Town of Alva.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to empower the North London Railway Company to construct a Railway from Liverpool Street in the City of London to join their existing Railway at Kingsland; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for enabling the Coleford, Monmouth, Usk, and Pontypool Railway Company to lease their Undertaking to the West Midland Railway Company; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for making a Railway from the Glasgow, Dumbarton, and Helensburgh Railway to Milngavie, and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for making a Railway from Lynn to Hunstanton, all in the County of Norfolk.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to confer on the Devon Valley Railway Company further Powers for the Completion of their Railway; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to authorize the Amalgamation of the Symington, Biggar, and Broughton Railway Company with the Caledonian Railway Company; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the Caledonian Railway Company to make a Branch Railway from Rutherglen to Coatbridge, with a Branch to Whifflat; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for making a Railway from Cocker mouth to Keswick and Penrith, with a Branch thereout, all in the County of Cumberland; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for enabling the Great Western Railway Company to make and maintain a Railway from Lightmoor to Coalbrookdale; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for making a Railway from Kirkcudbright to Castle Douglas, and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for making a Railway from the Cork and Bandon Railway near the City of Cork to the Town of Macroom in the County of Cork.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to empower the London and North-western Railway Company to make Railways at Burton-upon-Trent; to confer additional Powers upon them with reference to Parts of their Undertaking; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for extending the Periods for the Purchase of Lands and the Execution of Works for the Somerset Central Railway Company's authorized Railway from Glastonbury to Bruton; for authorizing the Somerset Central Railway Company to raise further Monies; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the South Wales Mineral Railway Company to extend their Railway to the Briton Ferry Docks; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for better supplying with Water the Borough of Stockport in the Counties of Chester and Lancaster, and the several Townships and Places adjacent or near thereto in those Counties; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for authorizing the Construction of Railways from the Severn Valley Railway to the West Midland Railway near Kidderminster, and the leasing of the Wellington and Severn Junction Railway by the Great Western and West Midland Railway Companies; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for making a Railway from the West Midland Railway at Bransford Bridge in the County of Worcester to the Shrewsbury and Hereford Railway near Leominster in the County of Hereford, and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to repeal and consolidate the several Acts relating to the Cornwall Railway Company; to empower them to make a Deviation Railway; to extend the Time for Completion of Parts of their Railway; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for granting further Powers to the Victoria Docks Gas Company.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for authorizing the Llanelly Railway and Dock Company to make and maintain additional Lines of Railway, and to raise further Monies; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for authorizing the Monmouthshire Railway and Canal Company to make and maintain new Lines of Railway and Deviations, and to acquire other Railways, and for authorizing them to raise additional Capital; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for authorizing a Lease or Sale of the Railway of the Saint Georges Harbour Company to the London and North-western Railway Company; and for reducing and regulating the Capital of the Saint Georges Harbour Company; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for making a Railway between the London and South-western Railway at or near to that Railway at Saint Denis near Southampton, and the Military Hospital at Netley, and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for extending the Stourbridge Railway to the Birmingham, Wolverhampton, and Stour Valley Railway at Smethwick, and for making a Branch Railway in connexion with the Stourbridge Railway; for authorizing Arrangements with other Companies; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the Swansea Harbour Trustees to raise a further Sum of Money for the Purposes of their Undertaking.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for making a Railway from the Oswestry and Newtown Railway at Oswestry to the London and North-western Railway at Whitchurch in the County of Salop, and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to extend and deviate a Portion of the Petersfield Railway.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to amalgamate the West of Fife Mineral Railway Company and the Charleston Railway and Harbour Company.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for authorizing the Rumney Railway Company to alter the Line and Levels of their existing Railway, and to make and maintain new Railways in connexion therewith; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the Caledonian Railway Company to make a Branch Railway from their Lesmahagow Line to Cot Castle near Stonehouse; to extend the Southfield Branch of that Line; to enlarge their Station at Symington; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the Caledonian Railway Company to extend their Cleland Branch to Morningside, and to make Branch Railways to Omoa Ironworks, to Drumbowie, and to Lanridge, all in the County of Lanark.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the Forth and Clyde Junction Railway Company to make a Branch Railway to Dalmonach Printworks in the County of Dumbarton, and to create additional Shares; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the Eastern Counties Railway Company to make new Lines of Railway; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the Kilkenny Junction Railway Company to abandon the Portion of their authorized Line between Abbeyleix and Mountrath, and instead thereof to make new Lines to the Maryborough Station and to the Roscrea Junction on the Great Southern and Western Railway; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for extending the Metropolitan Railway from Smithfield to Finsbury Circus; to authorize Arrangements with other Companies; to amend the Acts relating to the Metropolitan Railway; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for increasing the Capital of and conferring further Powers on the West London Extension Railway Company; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the Brecon and Merthyr Tydfil Junction Railway Company to make certain new Lines of Railway; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for establishing a separate System of Pilotage for the several Ports of Cardiff, Newport^ and Gloucester, in the Bristol Channel.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to increase the Capital of the Colne Valley and Halstead Railway Company, and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for providing and constructing Markets, Market Places, and Slaughterhouses, with all necessary Conveniences, within the Parishes of Saint Mary and Saint Bridget in the City of Dublin.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to authorize a Lease of the Margate Railway to the London, Chatham, and Dover Railway Company, and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the London, Chatham, and Dover Railway Company to make certain Deviations and Junction Lines of Railway; and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the Margate Railway Company to extend their Railway to Ramsgate; to change their Name; and for other Purposes connected with their Undertaking.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for making a Railway to connect Chard and Taunton in the County of Somerset, and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] West Hartlepool Harbour and Railway Traffic, &c.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to authorize the Construction of a Railway from the East Anglian Railways at Lynn to the Norwich and Spalding Railway at Sutton Bridge, and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for making Railways from Clara to Meelick in the King's County, Ireland, and for building a Bridge across the Shannon at Meelick.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for making a Railway from the Mold Branch of the Chester and Holyhead Railway at Mold to the Vale of Clwyd Railway, to be called "The Mold and Denbigh Junction Railway;" and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act for making a Railway from Lennoxtown of Campsie to Strathblane, with a Branch to Lettermill in the County of Stirling, and for other Purposes.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/24-25-vict-p03] An Act to enable the West Hartlepool Harbour and Railway Company to raise further Money; to amend the Acts relating to the Company; and for other Purposes.
