[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/31-geo-3-p02] An Act for the Encouragement of the Pilchard Fishery, by allowing a further Bounty upon Pilchards taken, cured, and exported.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/31-geo-3-p02] An Act for the better regulating of Gaols and other Places of Confinement.
