[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/31-geo-3-p02] An Act for granting to His Majesty a certain Sum of Money to be raised by a Lottery.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/31-geo-3-p02] An Act more effectually to prevent Abuses and Frauds committed by Persons employed in the Manufactures of combing Wool and Worsted Yarn, in the County of Norfolk, and City of Norwich, and County of the said City.
