[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/47-geo-3-sess-2-p01] This is a complete **list of acts of the Parliament of the United Kingdom for the year 1807**.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/47-geo-3-sess-2-p01] Acts passed from 1963 onwards are simply cited by calendar year and chapter number.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/47-geo-3-sess-2-p01] All modern acts have a short title, e.g.
[src:bristol-channel-pilot-cutter/47-geo-3-sess-2-p01] Some earlier acts also have a short title given to them by later acts, such as by the Short Titles Act 1896.
